                     <p class="- topic/p ">5V supply ok</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">On:</b> The internal 5V power supply is ok. Delivered
from the internal 15V power supply.</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Off:</b> Bypass mains not available or there is a hardware issue
