                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(E)</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry morerows="2" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">STATUS_1(D1242)</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry morerows="2" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">System firmware status indication</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p "> System firmware status indication. Shows what mode the
system is in:<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">On:</b> System is in Standby</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Off:</b> Bypass mains not available or there is a firmware or
wiring issue present.</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Check bypass mains power supply and connection.</p>
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Contact <xref conref="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.dita#Reference_Library-69E2C789/Reality_service_centers"
                              scope="local"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Slow flashing (0.5Hz):</b> System is in normal operation.</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Very fast flashing (4Hz):</b> The
system is in ISBS operation. There is an issue present with the main
controller, or the main controller was manually reset during operation.</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry morerows="1" class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Transfer the system to manual bypass,
for details see chapter <xref href="How_to_Switch_From_ISBS_Operation_to_Normal_Operation_CPT_0000356483.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Fast flashing (2Hz):</b> System is in bypass operation (over the
static switch), switched over by the main controller.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
               <row class="- topic/row ">
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(F)</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">STATUS_2(D1243)</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">ISBS status ok</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">On:</b> The ISBS system is ok and ready transfer to ISBS
operation if needed.</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Off:</b> Bypass mains not available or there is a firmware or
wiring issue present.</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Check bypass mains power supply and connection.</p>
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Contact <xref conref="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.dita#Reference_Library-69E2C789/Reality_service_centers"
                              scope="local"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
                  </entry>
               </row>
