                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">(G)</b>
                     </p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">STATUS_3(D1283)</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">ISBS operation active</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Off:</b> Indicated that the controller has not switched
to ISBS.</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">
                        <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">On:</b> The system is in ISBS operation. There is an issue present
with the main controller, or the main controller was manually reset
during operation.</p>
                  </entry>
                  <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                     <p class="- topic/p ">Transfer the system to manual bypass, for details see chapter <xref href="How_to_Switch_From_ISBS_Operation_to_Normal_Operation_CPT_0000356483.dita"
                              scope="local"
                              type="concept"
                              class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
                  </entry>
